caption.p: Chemical structure of the well-known alkaloids (nicotine (1), morphin (2), and caffeine (3)), such as those used in preclinical antioxidant studies (8-methoxy- N-methylflindersine (4), zanthodioline (5), alternamide A (6), alternamide B (7), alternamine A (8), hydroxytyrosol (9), formamide (10), alternamine B (11), uridine (12), mitraphylline (13), isomitraphylline (14), iraqiine (15), and kareemine (16)).
